==English==
{{was wotd|2008|February|8}}
===Etymology===
From 1980s {{m|en|Xeriscape}}, a term coined (and trademarked) by [[w:Denver Water|Denver Water]]. From {{confix|en|xeri|scape}}.
===Pronunciation===
* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|en|/ˈzɛ.ɹɪ.skeɪp/}}
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|en|/ˈzɛ.ɹə.skeɪp/}}
* {{audio|en|en-us-xeriscape.ogg|Audio (US)}}
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# A kind of [[landscape]] design for [[arid]] regions, minimising the need for [[irrigation]]. {{defdate|from 1980s}}
